OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777565468
OL,3,CPub murder accused felt 'ridiculed'
OL,4,Cbefore he fatally punched man, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA pub-goer has told a murder trial he
OL,8,Ffelt ridiculed by a group of people in
OL,9,Fa Leicestershire bar before he fatally
OL,10,Fpunched a 66-year-old grandfather as a
OL,11,F"pre-emptive strike".
OL,13,FNathan Gothard, 37, told jurors he
OL,14,F"lashed out" at David Darke outside
OL,15,Fthe Crown Inn in Appleby Magna,
OL,16,FLeicestershire, on the evening of 21
OL,17,FDecember last year because he was "in
OL,18,Ffear" of being attacked.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@TO]vD@AOUvD@LO]yD@cOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
