OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777565468
OL,3,CPub murder accused felt 'ridiculed'
OL,4,Cbefore he fatally punched man, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FGiving evidence at Leicester Crown
OL,8,FCourt today, Gothard said that after
OL,9,Fhe had been knocked to the ground by
OL,10,Fanother man, Mr Darke "violently"
OL,11,Fgrabbed him and threatened to kill him.
OL,13,FThe defendant, who denies murder and
OL,14,Fan alternative charge of manslaughter,
OL,15,Ftold the court he had drunk four or
OL,16,Ffive pints of San Miguel lager by the
OL,17,Ftime Mr Darke entered the pub as part
OL,18,Fof a group who had been at a staff
OL,19,FChristmas party.
OL,26,@rD@WOUrD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777565468
OL,3,CPub murder accused felt 'ridiculed'
OL,4,Cbefore he fatally punched man, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FGothard told the court he offered to
OL,8,Fbuy the group shots, which they
OL,9,Frefused, before he saw them laughing
OL,10,Fat him.
OL,12,F"I didn't want any trouble"
OL,14,FHe told the court: "It felt like I was
OL,15,Fbeing ridiculed. It just didn't feel
OL,16,Fright for some reason.
OL,18,F"When I turned around I would see them
OL,19,Fpointing and looking and laughing so I
OL,20,Fjust assumed it wasn't of a good
OL,21,Fnature."
OL,26,@vD@TOUzD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777565468
OL,3,CPub murder accused felt 'ridiculed'
OL,4,Cbefore he fatally punched man, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said Mr Darke was "aggressive"
OL,8,Ftowards him and grabbed his shoulder
OL,9,Fat the bar and "threatened to bury me
OL,10,Fand put me in the ground".
OL,12,FGothard told the jury: "I replied to
OL,13,Fhim that I didn't want any trouble and
OL,14,Fhe was older than my father, which he
OL,15,Fdidn't like."
OL,17,FHe said he thought Mr Darke's
OL,18,Fbehaviour was "uncalled for".
OL,26,@oD@VOUoD@aO]qD@POUrD@YO]tD@XOUwD@MO]zD@
OL,26,AOOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777565468
OL,3,CPub murder accused felt 'ridiculed'
OL,4,Cbefore he fatally punched man, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe defendant told the court the
OL,8,Flandlady asked him to leave the Crown
OL,9,FInn, adding: "I was a regular. Why
OL,10,Fshould I have to leave the pub when I
OL,11,Fhave done nothing wrong? It felt
OL,12,Funfair."
OL,14,FThe defendant said that outside the
OL,15,Fpub, Mr Darke was "berating" him and
OL,16,Fthe group "weren't talking in a nice
OL,17,Ftone" to him.
OL,26,@qD@NOUtD@HO]wD@SOUwD@\O]xD@KOUyD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777565468
OL,3,CPub murder accused felt 'ridiculed'
OL,4,Cbefore he fatally punched man, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FAsked by defence barrister Balraj
OL,8,FBhatia KC why he did not go home even
OL,9,Fthough he lived a "stone's throw" from
OL,10,Fthe pub, Gothard said it was "still
OL,11,Fearly" and he wanted to go back into
OL,12,Fthe bar.
OL,14,FJurors were shown CCTV of a man called
OL,15,FTy Fern knocking Gothard to the ground
OL,16,Fand kicking him outside the pub.
OL,18,FGothard told the jury he was "dazed
OL,19,Fand confused" after he was punched by
OL,20,FMr Fern, which knocked his glasses off
OL,21,Fhis head.
OL,26,@qD@SOUqD@aO]rD@^OUsD@FO]zD@^OU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777565468
OL,3,CPub murder accused felt 'ridiculed'
OL,4,Cbefore he fatally punched man, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said Mr Darke then grabbed him
OL,8,F"violently" as he stood up from the
OL,9,Fground.
OL,11,FGothard said Mr Darke repeated that he
OL,12,Fwould "bury him", adding: "It's a
OL,13,Fthreat to kill, I had to take it
OL,14,Fseriously. I was in fear, wasn't I?
OL,16,F"After he had threatened me, he's
OL,17,Fwalked quicker towards me to head me
OL,18,Foff.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@KO]tD@GOUtD@PO]tD@[OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777565468
OL,3,CPub murder accused felt 'ridiculed'
OL,4,Cbefore he fatally punched man, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"I have lashed out and hit him because
OL,8,FI thought I was going to be attacked
OL,9,Fagain. I threw a single punch. A pre-
OL,10,Femptive strike to stop being assaulted
OL,11,Fagain."
OL,13,F"Were you celebrating what you had
OL,14,Fjust done?"
OL,16,FAsked if he thought he may have
OL,17,Fseriously injured Mr Darke, Gothard
OL,18,Fsaid: "How he fell, yes. The sound."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@GO]uD@AOUzD@GOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777565468
OL,3,CPub murder accused felt 'ridiculed'
OL,4,Cbefore he fatally punched man, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FGothard, of Church Street, Appleby
OL,8,FMagna, denied "bouncing" around after
OL,9,Fhe punched Mr Darke.
OL,11,FIn cross-examination, prosecutor Peter
OL,12,FJoyce KC, asked: "Were you celebrating
OL,13,Fwhat you had just done to Mr Darke?"
OL,15,FGothard said: "No sir, I was concerned
OL,16,Fabout Mr Darke."
OL,18,FMr Joyce said Gothard made a woman
OL,19,Finside the pub "very, very
OL,20,Funcomfortable" by staring at her,
OL,21,Fwhich the defendant denied.
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@XO]tD@ROUuD@dO]wD@OOUxD@PO]{D@
OL,26,APOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777565468
OL,3,CPub murder accused felt 'ridiculed'
OL,4,Cbefore he fatally punched man, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe barrister asked: "It was obvious
OL,8,Fto everyone there that you were making
OL,9,Fthe whole group cross, wasn't it?", to
OL,10,Fwhich Gothard replied: "Not that I
OL,11,Frecall sir, no."
OL,13,FThe prosecutor told jurors on Tuesday
OL,14,Fthat there was a "menacing,
OL,15,Fthreatening, argumentative and
OL,16,Fdisputing" atmosphere in the pub
OL,17,Fbecause of Gothard's behaviour.
OL,26,@oD@VOUqD@bO]rD@XOUsD@PO]vD@ROUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
