PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777565468
OL,3,CPub murder accused felt 'ridiculed'
OL,4,Cbefore he fatally punched man, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe made inappropriate remarks to
OL,8,Fwomen, Mr Joyce had said, and made it
OL,9,Fclear to them "it was his terrain `
OL,10,Fthey were in his pub".
OL,12,FNathan Gothard denies murder and an
OL,13,Falternative count of manslaughter. The
OL,14,Ftrial continues.
